Description: Join us for Open Source Friday as we welcome Viral B. Shah, co-creator of the Julia Programming Language and CEO of JuliaHub, along with fellow creators Jeff Bezanson, Stefan Karpinski, and core contributor Keno Fischer! Julia is a powerful open source language that combines the ease of Python with C-like performance, designed for high-performance technical computing and scientific machine learning.
